OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start this
OL,6,Fmorning, but cloud will gradually
OL,7,Fbuild throughout the day. Some showery
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain possible by
OL,9,Flunchtime, before a band of more
OL,10,Fpersistent rain arrives in the west
OL,11,Flater. Feeling a little warmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain will
OL,14,Fgradually spread eastwards overnight,
OL,15,Fturning heavier and more persistent
OL,16,Flater in the night. A breezy but mild
OL,17,Fnight to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
