OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA wet morning with the rain
OL,6,Fheavy in places. The rain will slowly
OL,7,Fease from the west throughout the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Feeling cool for early
OL,10,FJune.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FStaying unsettled with a mixture of
OL,14,Fsunshine and showers on Tuesday and
OL,15,FWednesday, before turning wet and
OL,16,Fwindy on Thursday. Temperatures around
OL,17,For a little below average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
